{"tid":351474,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友同我講佢唔上連登","createTime":"2017-08-08T05:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T20:56:18.000Z","uid":89985,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7bdeb8da6d9582063aa1c250d5f4c07b75cc865a","tid":351474,"uid":89985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:42:14.000Z","msg":"同女朋友一齊就半年<br />\n佢同我講過佢唔會上連登<br />\n但有日偷睇佢手機發現佢有上連登有ac<br />\n平時好乖乖女好斯文<br />\n但佢原來係藍絲<br />\n啲post講嘅嘢仲粗俗過我<br />\n點解要呃我唔同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b591a0f3a9dfa65be404d54c98d8416fe07c0a3","tid":351474,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:42:50.000Z","msg":"關你撚事"},{"pid":"697314dc62a1df68d3247abe3710d72fd4689cd3","tid":351474,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:43:30.000Z","msg":"小妹都係咁樣呃條仔"},{"pid":"c43bd8f2db53fb86bae9e8dffb6d08697164478e","tid":351474,"uid":37752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:44:50.000Z","msg":"同你一辛苦，俾人發洩下啦<br />\n屌你"},{"pid":"1ec015f3ddc7b72564058a7a8acdb935ebc1f02f","tid":351474,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:45:30.000Z","msg":"日日對住佢講連登嘢<br />\n佢想搭嗲又要扮唔知係乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa02cc13c92c5427de4a1191fb237bba6fbd7029","tid":351474,"uid":89985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:07:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小妹都係咁樣呃條仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n既然大家都有上點解唔講 有嘢笑一齊笑都好啊 我唔明點解要呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abd7cb85644a673698f68c22d4aca6a3e420f5b","tid":351474,"uid":89985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:15:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日日對住佢講連登嘢<br />\n佢想搭嗲又要扮唔知係乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有啊 我對住佢成日講 佢就敷衍我笑下就算 好似不大興趣 點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8f2c9666b8dc07cc99f1a225f126216f73b4af","tid":351474,"uid":68370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T20:55:01.000Z","msg":"佢唔想比你見到佢俗果面，驚你唔開心/破壞你對佢既印象 。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41d92bc32b84e7c0b2a872f1733d069528fa871","tid":351474,"uid":68370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T20:56:18.000Z","msg":"佢唔想你知 你咪配合下囉 小事"}]}